It's true.

6
00:01:42,390 --> 00:01:44,350
Wei Ruolai pled guilty on the spot

7
00:01:44,350 --> 00:01:45,870
and was dragged to the execution ground.

8
00:01:45,870 --> 00:01:46,750
What?

9
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:49,110
