13
00:01:53,610 --> 00:01:54,470
Thanks, Mr. Yu.

14
00:01:54,940 --> 00:01:56,190
It might be too late.

15
00:01:56,450 --> 00:01:57,130
I'll

16
00:01:57,150 --> 00:01:58,430
send someone over.

17
00:01:58,430 --> 00:01:59,110
But...

18
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:25,560
Any last words?

19
00:02:29,110 --> 00:02:29,910
Wei Ruolai.

20
00:02:30,430 --> 00:02:32,350
If you identify the mastermind,

21
00:02:32,970 --> 00:02:33,930
your sentence

22
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:35,530
will be reduced.

23
00:02:37,410 --> 00:02:38,870
Targeting Mr. Shen again?

24
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:41,800
Didn't he ask you to do it this time?

25
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,390
Don't bother.

26
00:02:44,410 --> 00:02:45,490
Just shoot me.

27
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:47,510
Wei Ruolai.

28
00:02:48,470 --> 00:02:49,820
So many are envious of

29
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:51,380
how far you've come

30
00:02:51,420 --> 00:02:53,420
without money or a good background.

31
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:57,300
Why did you risk your bright future

32
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,610
in Central Bank?

33
00:02:58,640 --> 00:03:00,390
You were well fed and safe

34
00:03:00,420 --> 00:03:01,430
in prison.

35
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:04,230
Why did you join the Dare-to-Die Corps?

36
00:03:04,530 --> 00:03:05,730
For the country.

37
00:03:05,830 --> 00:03:06,430
Me too.

38
00:03:06,430 --> 00:03:07,030
Nonsense!

39
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:09,620
You're just disrupting the social order

40
00:03:09,650 --> 00:03:11,030
and ruining the government's reputation!

41
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:13,290
Did I ruin the government's reputation?

42
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:15,360
How can you say that as a police?

43
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,160
The people's money is used

44
00:03:17,180 --> 00:03:18,390
to wipe out communists.

45
00:03:18,390 --> 00:03:20,310
The people benefit in the end!

46
00:03:21,270 --> 00:03:22,950
Do you really believe that?

47
00:03:23,350 --> 00:03:24,180
Stupid!

48
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:30,490
Execute him!

49
00:03:40,270 --> 00:03:41,020
Hide!

50
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:48,910
Drive forward.

51
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,030
Go there, Congyun!

52
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:52,430
Sir, there are gunshots!

53
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:53,870
Ruolai's in danger!

54
00:03:53,870 --> 00:03:55,510
Only your survival

55
00:03:55,820 --> 00:03:57,240
matters to me!

56
00:03:57,550 --> 00:03:58,180
Congyun!

57
00:04:02,220 --> 00:04:03,880
Punish Wei Ruolai on the spot.

58
00:04:17,269 --> 00:04:17,800
Boss!

59
00:04:18,350 --> 00:04:19,190
Watch out!

60
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:32,230
Sir.

61
00:04:33,530 --> 00:04:34,320
Sir.

62
00:04:34,970 --> 00:04:35,480
Sir.

63
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,220
It's dangerous!

64
00:04:36,220 --> 00:04:36,690
Sir.

65
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,290
Sir.

66
00:05:23,030 --> 00:05:23,650
Let's go.

67
00:05:32,100 --> 00:05:33,300
They're all dead.

68
00:05:34,630 --> 00:05:35,760
Ruolai isn't there.

69
00:06:27,910 --> 00:06:28,710
Come in.

70
00:06:53,990 --> 00:06:54,790
Thank you.

71
00:06:56,350 --> 00:06:57,280
You're welcome.

72
00:06:58,030 --> 00:06:58,590
Wait.

73
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,030
You should thank me first.

74
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:03,480
I asked Miss Shen for help.

75
00:07:03,790 --> 00:07:05,910
If it weren't for me, you'd have been killed by that car.

76
00:07:05,910 --> 00:07:06,390
Okay.

77
00:07:06,390 --> 00:07:07,000
Got it.

78
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,020
Get what?

79
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:09,150
Where are your manners?

80
00:07:09,150 --> 00:07:10,350
Thank you!

81
00:07:10,350 --> 00:07:11,550
Stop arguing.

82
00:07:11,820 --> 00:07:13,110
The priority is

83
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:15,710
for you two to leave Shanghai now.

84
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,430
No.

85
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:17,830
I can't leave.

86
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:19,830
Those criminals are still at large.

87
00:07:19,910 --> 00:07:20,950
That's a long

88
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:22,790
and arduous task.

89
00:07:22,790 --> 00:07:23,830
You can't do it

90
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:25,070
on your own.

91
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:27,550
Lin Qiaosong failed the mission today.

92
00:07:27,550 --> 00:07:28,230
Next,

93
00:07:28,270 --> 00:07:29,590
he'll do anything

94
00:07:29,590 --> 00:07:30,710
to catch you two.

95
00:07:30,730 --> 00:07:31,780
At least

96
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,400
think about Chunmiao.

97
00:07:36,350 --> 00:07:37,210
How about this?

98
00:07:37,710 --> 00:07:38,640
You go back first

99
00:07:38,790 --> 00:07:40,630
and tell my father...

100
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:42,820
Wei Ruolai!

101
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:43,330
Ouch!

102
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,120
Wen's dead

103
00:07:44,390 --> 00:07:45,120
and Ms. Zhou

104
00:07:45,150 --> 00:07:45,790
lost her mind,

105
00:07:45,790 --> 00:07:46,510
so

106
00:07:46,510 --> 00:07:46,990
you've

107
00:07:46,990 --> 00:07:47,990
given up on life.

108
00:07:48,340 --> 00:07:49,630
I understand that.

109
00:07:49,810 --> 00:07:51,430
But please follow some rules!

110
00:07:51,430 --> 00:07:52,909
Take your own advice!

111
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:54,820
At least I'm not so dumb to get caught

112
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:56,080
and need others' help.

113
00:07:58,270 --> 00:07:59,040
Wei Ruolai.

114
00:07:59,310 --> 00:08:00,800
If you stay in Shanghai,

115
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:02,520
you won't live past a month.

116
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:03,860
I risked it

117
00:08:03,910 --> 00:08:05,430
to save you this time.

118
00:08:05,430 --> 00:08:07,340
I might not be so lucky next time.

119
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:09,310
Those people are still at large.

120
00:08:09,310 --> 00:08:10,310
Even if you die,

121
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:11,390
it'd be in vain.

122
00:08:13,580 --> 00:08:14,610
You should know

123
00:08:15,150 --> 00:08:16,030
Jiangxi Soviet

124
00:08:16,290 --> 00:08:18,100
has its own bank now.

125
00:08:18,230 --> 00:08:18,950
What we lack

126
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:20,880
is financial talents like you.

127
00:08:21,110 --> 00:08:22,170
They even provide

128
00:08:22,390 --> 00:08:23,790
food and uniforms.

129
00:08:31,140 --> 00:08:32,980
Stop hesitating.

130
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,880
Miss Shen saved your life,

131
00:08:34,990 --> 00:08:37,450
so your life belongs to the Communist Party.

132
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:45,860
Okay.

133
00:08:47,190 --> 00:08:48,350
Tomorrow at 9 a.m.,

134
00:08:48,370 --> 00:08:50,580
I'll come with info of the route and handler,

135
00:08:50,580 --> 00:08:51,720
so you can evacuate.

136
00:08:52,580 --> 00:08:53,300
Thank you.

137
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:55,160
Aren't you coming with us?

138
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,740
I'm not exposed yet.

139
00:08:56,880 --> 00:08:58,250
I can stay here longer.

140
00:09:01,430 --> 00:09:02,130
Ruolai.

141
00:09:02,230 --> 00:09:03,030
Don't worry.

142
00:09:03,300 --> 00:09:05,380
You can't keep a good man down.

143
00:09:06,230 --> 00:09:07,440
At Jiangxi Soviet,

144
00:09:07,710 --> 00:09:08,510
you'll

145
00:09:08,510 --> 00:09:10,040
kick off your career again.

146
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,850
You acted on your own again.

147
00:09:17,020 --> 00:09:17,340
You...

148
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:18,860
Without my help,

149
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:21,030
Ruolai would've been killed.

150
00:09:21,510 --> 00:09:22,510
Saving him

151
00:09:22,690 --> 00:09:25,120
benefits Jiangxi Soviet.

152
00:09:25,630 --> 00:09:26,430
What?

153
00:09:27,430 --> 00:09:29,490
He's willing to go to Jiangxi Soviet?

154
00:09:30,430 --> 00:09:31,030
Good.

155
00:09:31,270 --> 00:09:32,030
Good.

156
00:09:36,020 --> 00:09:37,220
This is the route map.

157
00:09:37,330 --> 00:09:39,390
Tell him to leave Shanghai tomorrow.

158
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:46,390
Actually, there's one more person

159
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:47,500
this time,

160
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,800
Niu Chunmiao.

161
00:09:51,190 --> 00:09:52,180
You...

162
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,870
Don't be angry.

163
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:56,670
She's really great.

164
00:09:56,670 --> 00:09:57,820
I really like her.

165
00:09:58,260 --> 00:09:59,590
She's still a stranger.

166
00:09:59,700 --> 00:10:00,250
Wait.

167
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,630
Where's your discipline?

168
00:10:03,010 --> 00:10:04,020
Listen to me.

169
00:10:04,050 --> 00:10:04,810
Didn't you

170
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,560
ask me to work on Ruolai?

171
00:10:06,590 --> 00:10:07,700
I bumped into her

172
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:10,080
at Ruolai's house once when he wasn't in.

173
00:10:10,350 --> 00:10:10,960
She even

174
00:10:11,160 --> 00:10:12,680
wanted to spend 50 silver dollars

175
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:14,020
to sell Ruolai to me.

176
00:10:14,590 --> 00:10:17,490
So you came to Shanghai

177
00:10:17,750 --> 00:10:20,150
to get your marriage with Ruolai annulled?

178
00:10:22,190 --> 00:10:23,640
What's your type then?

179
00:10:26,340 --> 00:10:28,120
I like someone like Liao Si.

180
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:30,620
-Liao...
-He's a truly

181
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,830
upright hero.

182
00:10:34,170 --> 00:10:35,560
Who is Liao Si?

183
00:10:37,630 --> 00:10:39,150
He used to pick herbs.

184
00:10:39,870 --> 00:10:40,930
He was my neighbor.

185
00:10:40,990 --> 00:10:42,030
But now,

186
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:46,140
he's in the Red Army.

187
00:10:49,430 --> 00:10:50,310
Red Army?

188
00:10:51,890 --> 00:10:54,120
Neat and frail scholars like Wei Ruolai

189
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:55,220
might be

190
00:10:55,250 --> 00:10:57,050
popular with women in your city.

191
00:10:57,110 --> 00:10:58,600
But not in

192
00:10:59,110 --> 00:11:00,190
my hometown.

193
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:02,260
My mom likes him a lot.

194
00:11:02,390 --> 00:11:03,670
But I didn't agree.

195
00:11:04,300 --> 00:11:05,470
I came to Shanghai

196
00:11:05,510 --> 00:11:06,670
to make money

197
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:07,840
for my dowry.

198
00:11:08,070 --> 00:11:10,590
Then I'll go to the mountains to find Liao Si.

199
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:14,560
What if Liao Si doesn't like you?

200
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:21,080
I'll join the Red Army

201
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:23,490
and marry another member.

202
00:11:24,100 --> 00:11:25,830
She wants to be a Red Army member

203
00:11:25,940 --> 00:11:27,620
and marry a member.

204
00:11:28,330 --> 00:11:29,850
How can I refuse her?

205
00:11:32,980 --> 00:11:34,150
All right, go.

206
00:11:35,580 --> 00:11:36,530
No longer angry?

207
00:11:38,510 --> 00:11:39,520
Thank you, Mr. Xu.

208
00:11:42,140 --> 00:11:42,910
The qin!

209
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:44,070
Okay.

210
00:11:44,220 --> 00:11:44,920
Take it.

211
00:11:47,210 --> 00:11:47,850
Bye.

212
00:12:02,310 --> 00:12:02,910
When we

213
00:12:03,210 --> 00:12:04,540
return to our hometown,

214
00:12:04,850 --> 00:12:06,560
can we both join the party?

215
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:13,190
You don't know this.

216
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:16,900
Since we've done so much work,

217
00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:19,030
they must accept us.

218
00:12:25,350 --> 00:12:26,230
You don't like

219
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:28,280
the Communist Party?

220
00:12:29,670 --> 00:12:30,510
No.

221
00:12:31,430 --> 00:12:32,240
I just...

222
00:12:32,260 --> 00:12:34,340
don't know much about it yet.

223
00:12:35,430 --> 00:12:36,830
But I do!

224
00:12:37,230 --> 00:12:38,550
Ask me anything.

225
00:12:38,590 --> 00:12:40,440
I know many Red Army members.

226
00:12:40,590 --> 00:12:42,110
They're all heroes.

227
00:12:44,730 --> 00:12:46,100
Don't worry, Doggie.

228
00:12:46,430 --> 00:12:48,230
You'll find out

229
00:12:48,230 --> 00:12:50,430
why our village's youths

230
00:12:50,450 --> 00:12:53,260
are so eager to join the Red Army.

231
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,250
Sleep early.

232
00:12:57,790 --> 00:12:59,190
We're leaving tomorrow.

233
00:13:32,310 --> 00:13:33,110
Jinzhen.

234
00:13:45,510 --> 00:13:46,230
Brother.

235
00:13:47,230 --> 00:13:48,150
Still up?

236
00:13:48,510 --> 00:13:49,580
I was waiting for you.

237
00:13:49,580 --> 00:13:50,380
For me?

238
00:13:52,790 --> 00:13:53,070
Sit.

239
00:13:53,070 --> 00:13:53,870
Drink with me.

240
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:57,240
Why are you drinking?

241
00:14:10,870 --> 00:14:13,590
Why are you drinking in the middle of the night?

242
00:14:21,830 --> 00:14:22,960
Are you in a bad mood?

243
00:14:23,710 --> 00:14:25,440
Where did you go during the day?

244
00:14:26,590 --> 00:14:27,310
Just the arsenal

245
00:14:27,310 --> 00:14:27,890
for work.

246
00:14:27,910 --> 00:14:28,470
Why?

247
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:46,400
I found this shell

248
00:14:46,490 --> 00:14:49,210
by the sniping spot near the execution ground.

249
00:14:49,510 --> 00:14:50,630
If I'm right,

250
00:14:51,880 --> 00:14:53,280
the gun is in the qin case.

251
00:15:00,460 --> 00:15:01,900
I saw the person's back

252
00:15:02,260 --> 00:15:03,790
but I wasn't sure it was you.

253
00:15:05,070 --> 00:15:06,820
But I remember the qin box.

254
00:15:08,430 --> 00:15:09,230
It looks

255
00:15:10,510 --> 00:15:11,670
just like this one.

256
00:15:13,610 --> 00:15:15,140
What are you talking about?

257
00:15:26,400 --> 00:15:28,040
You saved Ruolai's life.

258
00:15:31,460 --> 00:15:32,260
Thank you.

259
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:35,860
It has nothing to do with me.

260
00:15:35,860 --> 00:15:37,010
He was lucky.

261
00:15:38,950 --> 00:15:39,810
Anything else?

262
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:41,080
If not,

263
00:15:41,110 --> 00:15:41,910
I'm tired.

264
00:15:42,230 --> 00:15:42,830
Rest early.

265
00:15:42,830 --> 00:15:44,670
Be careful in the future.

266
00:15:45,290 --> 00:15:46,720
These shells are all evidence.

267
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:48,180
It's easy to investigate.

268
00:15:48,190 --> 00:15:49,310
After Ruolai leaves,

269
00:15:49,310 --> 00:15:50,870
they'll search our house.

270
00:15:50,870 --> 00:15:52,930
If they find the gun, you're done for.

271
00:15:53,710 --> 00:15:54,610
What are you on about?

272
00:15:54,610 --> 00:15:56,490
Don't leave the gun at home

273
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,190
and implicate the family.

274
00:15:58,190 --> 00:15:59,310
You have to at least

275
00:16:00,150 --> 00:16:00,950
consider

276
00:16:00,950 --> 00:16:03,010
your sister-in-law and Yu's safety.

277
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:15,680
Reassured now?

278
00:16:17,230 --> 00:16:18,060
Good night.

279
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:37,160
You mean Shen Tunan was there too?

280
00:16:38,490 --> 00:16:39,920
He drove there.

281
00:16:40,150 --> 00:16:41,430
He didn't get injured

282
00:16:41,900 --> 00:16:42,870
from the shootout.

283
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:45,010
So I suspect the sniper's related to him.

284
00:16:45,010 --> 00:16:46,180
We've confirmed

285
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,660
his sister's a communist.

286
00:16:47,900 --> 00:16:49,100
Shen Tunan...

287
00:16:49,130 --> 00:16:49,930
Mr. Kang.

288
00:16:50,310 --> 00:16:51,590
Whether he is or not,

289
00:16:51,610 --> 00:16:53,090
he hurt so many of us.

290
00:16:53,270 --> 00:16:54,500
He must pay the price.

291
00:16:56,550 --> 00:16:58,550
Learn to prioritize things.

292
00:16:58,870 --> 00:17:00,680
Public opinion can't be suppressed now.

293
00:17:00,680 --> 00:17:02,050
The higher-ups are furious.

294
00:17:02,050 --> 00:17:03,980
The only way to appease them

295
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:06,290
is to arrest communists.

296
00:17:06,520 --> 00:17:07,750
The more, the better.

297
00:17:10,109 --> 00:17:12,119
My only clue is Shen Jinzhen.

298
00:17:12,150 --> 00:17:12,790
Before,

299
00:17:13,170 --> 00:17:14,270
I couldn't arrest her.

