00:34:20,310 --> 00:34:21,440
The Communist Party

598
00:34:21,580 --> 00:34:23,659
was born to create a new world.

599
00:34:23,820 --> 00:34:25,840
The unreasonable things in the world

600
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:27,800
should be reformed

601
00:34:27,830 --> 00:34:29,230
and rebuilt!

602
00:34:29,330 --> 00:34:29,969
For that,

603
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:31,550
every communist

604
00:34:31,570 --> 00:34:33,179
can sacrifice their life!

605
00:34:44,850 --> 00:34:45,650
Brother.

606
00:34:47,070 --> 00:34:47,940
I have to go.

607
00:34:50,320 --> 00:34:51,650
If you want to arrest me,

608
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:55,030
now's the time.

609
00:34:56,260 --> 00:34:57,010
Otherwise,

610
00:34:57,930 --> 00:34:59,730
we can only meet again

611
00:35:01,190 --> 00:35:02,450
after the revolution.

612
00:35:36,270 --> 00:35:37,230
Shen Jinzhen!

613
00:35:37,520 --> 00:35:38,900
-Come out!
-What are you doing?

614
00:35:38,900 --> 00:35:40,420
What are you doing?

615
00:35:41,540 --> 00:35:42,110
Shut up!

616
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:43,390
You bandits!

617
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:44,590
-Search!
-Yes!

618
00:35:44,590 --> 00:35:45,390
What are you doing?

619
00:35:45,390 --> 00:35:46,850
Mr. Shen won't let you off!

620
00:35:50,340 --> 00:35:51,140
Shut up!

621
00:35:52,020 --> 00:35:52,900
Don't cry.

622
00:35:54,940 --> 00:35:55,700
Don't cry

623
00:35:56,520 --> 00:35:57,720
Biao, she's not here.

624
00:36:00,070 --> 00:36:01,270
Biao, she's not here.

625
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:03,280
Biao, no one's here.

626
00:36:10,690 --> 00:36:11,250
Boss.

627
00:36:11,350 --> 00:36:12,110
Only

628
00:36:12,560 --> 00:36:13,840
the housekeeper is at home.

629
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:15,170
That means she ran away.

630
00:36:15,790 --> 00:36:16,890
Inform Mr. Kang now!

631
00:36:16,890 --> 00:36:17,350
Yes.

632
00:36:17,530 --> 00:36:18,490
Station more men

633
00:36:18,590 --> 00:36:19,750
with Shen Jinzhen's photo

634
00:36:19,750 --> 00:36:21,680
at the station and the dock!

635
00:36:21,870 --> 00:36:22,390
Yes!

636
00:36:23,460 --> 00:36:24,780
Even if you die,

637
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:26,790
don't let Shen Jinzhen leave Shanghai!

638
00:36:26,790 --> 00:36:27,520
Yes!

639
00:36:29,530 --> 00:36:32,450
You'll die a horrible death!

640
00:36:32,790 --> 00:36:34,670
Mr. Shen won't spare you!

641
00:37:01,280 --> 00:37:02,040
Jinzhen!

642
00:37:06,270 --> 00:37:06,940
Get in.

643
00:37:20,350 --> 00:37:21,480
Where are you going?

644
00:37:22,600 --> 00:37:24,000
Ruolai's waiting for me.

645
00:37:25,130 --> 00:37:26,510
I have to send them out.

646
00:37:31,620 --> 00:37:33,110
The officers are everywhere.

647
00:37:33,110 --> 00:37:35,040
You can't hide from them like this.

648
00:37:38,490 --> 00:37:39,620
I'll give you a ride.

649
00:38:29,110 --> 00:38:29,700
Go!

650
00:38:29,740 --> 00:38:30,150
Yes.

651
00:38:31,950 --> 00:38:32,610
Don't move.

652
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:37,860
What are you doing?

653
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:39,540
Don't move. Get up the stairs.

654
00:38:39,860 --> 00:38:40,860
Who are you?

655
00:38:43,030 --> 00:38:43,570
Turn left.

656
00:38:43,570 --> 00:38:44,340
Be gentle!

657
00:38:44,760 --> 00:38:45,520
Don't move.

658
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:51,660
Mr. Qian?

659
00:38:52,270 --> 00:38:53,070
Mr. Qian.

660
00:38:53,560 --> 00:38:54,620
Long time no see.

661
00:38:55,010 --> 00:38:56,480
Y-You want to see me?

662
00:38:57,350 --> 00:38:58,140
Compatriot.

663
00:38:58,810 --> 00:38:59,930
Long time no see.

664
00:39:00,370 --> 00:39:02,210
Then why did you arrest us?

665
00:39:02,230 --> 00:39:03,040
Shut up.

666
00:39:04,200 --> 00:39:04,730
Mr. Qian.

667
00:39:04,750 --> 00:39:05,200
Mr. Qian.

668
00:39:05,200 --> 00:39:06,560
Why are you doing this?

669
00:39:07,380 --> 00:39:08,150
Mr. Qian.

670
00:39:12,070 --> 00:39:13,300
You're a communist.

671
00:39:15,310 --> 00:39:16,790
Not yet.

672
00:39:16,790 --> 00:39:17,920
But soon.

673
00:39:17,940 --> 00:39:18,820
Soon...

674
00:39:20,020 --> 00:39:21,130
Maybe.

675
00:39:21,410 --> 00:39:22,230
Just arrest me.

676
00:39:22,230 --> 00:39:23,550
Let her go.

677
00:39:23,870 --> 00:39:25,670
If I hand you to the authorities,

678
00:39:25,680 --> 00:39:26,640
I'd get

679
00:39:26,940 --> 00:39:28,140
500 silver dollars.

680
00:39:28,170 --> 00:39:29,280
I'll give you 1,000!

681
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:30,280
Let us go!

682
00:39:32,040 --> 00:39:33,560
You're that rich?

683
00:39:34,470 --> 00:39:35,590
I don't have it now.

684
00:39:35,970 --> 00:39:37,770
I'll pay you back slowly later.

685
00:39:38,290 --> 00:39:40,650
500 silver dollars is nothing.

686
00:39:43,770 --> 00:39:44,610
I arrested you

687
00:39:46,130 --> 00:39:47,890
to ask you for a favor.

688
00:39:53,030 --> 00:39:54,150
What is it?

689
00:39:58,840 --> 00:40:01,440
Kuomintang has been playing with fire lately.

690
00:40:02,140 --> 00:40:04,260
I need to leave a way out for myself.

691
00:40:05,020 --> 00:40:06,820
I'm making friends

692
00:40:08,340 --> 00:40:10,020
with a communist.

693
00:40:13,260 --> 00:40:14,080
Changsheng.

694
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:24,240
My family is in Shanghai.

695
00:40:24,870 --> 00:40:25,730
In my hometown,

696
00:40:26,070 --> 00:40:27,870
I have neighbors and relatives.

697
00:40:28,210 --> 00:40:29,910
If you become powerful,

698
00:40:29,990 --> 00:40:32,020
please look out for me and my people.

699
00:40:33,960 --> 00:40:34,840
Okay.

700
00:40:50,560 --> 00:40:51,760
I've known Xu

701
00:40:53,480 --> 00:40:55,120
for more than three years.

702
00:40:56,640 --> 00:40:58,680
Although he looked serious

703
00:40:58,790 --> 00:41:00,110
and stern,

704
00:41:01,870 --> 00:41:02,700
he actually

705
00:41:03,870 --> 00:41:05,220
had a soft heart.

706
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,010
He never

707
00:41:10,890 --> 00:41:11,960
got married

708
00:41:13,040 --> 00:41:14,320
or had children.

709
00:41:17,790 --> 00:41:19,640
He treated me like a daughter.

710
00:41:21,690 --> 00:41:23,490
He often cooked good food for me.

711
00:41:25,870 --> 00:41:27,310
He nagged sometimes.

712
00:41:28,860 --> 00:41:30,220
He had no hobbies,

713
00:41:31,990 --> 00:41:34,850
except listening to Peking opera and drinking wine

714
00:41:35,140 --> 00:41:36,140
every so often.

715
00:41:44,270 --> 00:41:45,590
His biggest wish

716
00:41:48,230 --> 00:41:50,700
was to see the Red Army enter Shanghai

717
00:41:53,470 --> 00:41:55,190
and witness the victory.

718
00:42:13,190 --> 00:42:14,070
I'm sorry,

719
00:42:14,420 --> 00:42:14,950
Brother.

720
00:42:35,310 --> 00:42:35,960
Stop!

721
00:42:37,620 --> 00:42:39,350
We're officers! Open the door!

722
00:42:42,660 --> 00:42:43,990
It's a temporary check.

723
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:45,060
Please cooperate.

724
00:42:50,270 --> 00:42:50,910
You...

725
00:42:53,790 --> 00:42:54,920
Where are you going?

726
00:42:55,630 --> 00:42:56,130
Show your ticket!
